The paper discusses the effectiveness of parameter selection mechanisms in evolutionary computation, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.NE). The paper also deals with optimization problems, which are relevant to the subfields of machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper proposes a simple update rule for parameter selection, which could be relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
